Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(500,500)\blur4\fs40}本字幕由咖啡君手抄自幻樱字幕组，修正少量翻译错误，仅供试看。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,会哭叫说明你没做好觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这群小子 都给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个年代看到了老人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,记得把他们当成幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真是受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,从前茨户这个驿站街被日泥一家控制
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可是他们的手下久寿田马吉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,自己另开了一家赌场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,自那以后两边整天就杀来杀去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是保镖吧 看脸就能猜出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,想给哪边卖命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还没定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 你见没见过这里有男人文着奇怪的文身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.63,0:00:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,文身?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:00:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,黑道的文身这里到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不是黑道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,给 边见和雄的复印文身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:45.31,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\pos(1421.05,851.2)\blur7.5}诳惑之狐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.81,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)\t(0,500,\c&HFFFFFF&)\blur7.5\pos(1421.05,851.2)}诳惑之狐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你这种冒失鬼是怎么骗过杉元偷印文身的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还装傻 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:03:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,家永 竟然活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你还敢带他看医生 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没给医生看他的文身 只是借地方躲一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这种人有必要留他一条命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,该不会…你看上他了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,少胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好救了他 我在他这里打听到了一个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,家永 告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,消防队和警察好像都没找到死伤者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,地下室的尸体也埋在了瓦砾下面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那两个人真的死了 可能会在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,白石说 爆炸的那一刻家永和牛山也在二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,应该不会被埋往地下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说不定没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,记得把那鱼板扔了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,白石那小子 把我刚买的炸药全用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.62,Explain,,0,0,0,,札幌著名的商业街和娱乐街
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,估计是薄野吧 那个色和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要钱重新买炸药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,附近的长沼有个科坦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有我的亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里打猎赚钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,看 杉元上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抓到奇隆努普 也就是北狐了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,用棍子打死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你一棍子解决啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这个陷阱是用旧油桶钉上三寸钉做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,只要狐狸伸头去舔桶底的油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就会被卡住 拔不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,据传 红毛狐狸等天气暖和了就会出来害人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们把红狐狸叫伊卡卡拉奇隆努普
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是诳惑之狐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,狐狸皮一张大概一元钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,水獭皮的价格差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,棕熊皮今年能卖五元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,虾夷松鼠更便宜 一张二十钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一条狐狸能换六瓶酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是没浪费那些炸药 我们现在早就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙想气死我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,杉元 还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这个男人在札幌…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,基罗兄 不用往下说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他找阿希莉帕借钱 结果全输在赌马里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你真说了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,冲啊冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,完了 完了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你把那钱用在赌博上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,给我舔桶底的油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,只能在这里待一阵子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是芙奇的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,六兄弟之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:03.09,ainu,,0,0,0,,最近总是来些意想不到的客人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他会收留我们住在这户七赛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,上次也是 有个奇怪的女人住进了这个村子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,据说她能看到过去和未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,村子里的人都被她害得脑子不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,正好来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫茵卡拉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,几位尼西帕长得可真英俊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫白石由竹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,单身 没有女友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 您头上在流血呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,有人把带钉子的油桶盖在我头上嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我对有伤疤的男人最没抵抗力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那位军人大哥也很有男子气概呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这…过奖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.94,ainu,,0,0,0,,衫元会把屎放汤里吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 不嫌臭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,阿希莉帕姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才是不是把杉元 哦哈乌和欧索玛放一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,又在说我吃屎对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,从小樽来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是听别人说太叔父在小樽有很多亲戚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,知道你们是谁 或者在找什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,厉害 你说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我很擅长占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这种占卜叫尼沃库
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,阿伊努人不论事情大小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们不知道该如何判断的时候 就会依靠占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,并且把占卜的结果视作神的旨意 绝不坏疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,希拉奇卡姆依
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,用于占卜的狐狸头骨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我家祖传的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:08:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是灵力最强的白狐的头骨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,占卜时首先将下颚放在头上 接着慢慢低头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,根据骨头掉在地上时的状况占卜吉凶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果牙齿向上就是吉兆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我来算算你们能不能找到要找的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,牙齿朝下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无希望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,前途或有凶险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,应该立刻罢手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这些话可以套用在任何事情上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是在随口胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不信什么占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是新时代的阿伊努女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,占卜终究是占卜 不是指示命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 你们要找的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是随口胡说 请不要放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的伊卡卡拉奇隆努普
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女人的占卜出奇地准
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,村民们好像给了她不少贡品 脑子不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是这样在各地的村子招摇撞骗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还是没找到白石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道白石去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,茵卡拉玛妹子 让我发大财吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣 玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,来选马吧 该茵卡拉玛妹子出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那匹马怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有了 就是那匹马
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,希拉奇卡姆依说4号马会有好运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没有算错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我的希拉奇卡姆依不会说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,白石先生 我这里有个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这个护身符叫艾卡艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,戴在手上就能消灾解难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢茵卡拉玛妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,二十钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要是这把输了我就真成穷光蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,4号 4号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,冲 冲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样冲过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,赢了 我真的赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你太厉害了 茵卡拉玛妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好 下一场比赛也麻烦你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,白石先生 我这里有个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是牛皮消的根
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,味道非常难闻 常用于辟邪驱魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,七十钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,买了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,下场比赛赢的会是2号马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好 全看你了 2号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,拉屎王和红狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 白石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我说怎么闻到一股穷酸味 原来是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,白石你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,明明欠了阿希莉帕姑娘的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还有胆子来赛马场赌博啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,欠钱?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,多少来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,两元?三元?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,喏 去捡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒 白石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,靠占卜赌博 以后会倒大霉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,别被这个母狐狸骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你骂谁母狐狸 放肆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,叫茵卡拉玛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,口气臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,下一场赢的不是3号就是4号吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,基罗兰克也会占卜?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在马背上长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因为了解马匹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,日俄战争中工兵部队的所有马匹都是我在照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,的确 狐狸头骨也说会是3号赢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,3号是吧 我去买
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,站住 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里啊 高崎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,找你好久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 根本不是这个人吧 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,高崎哪有这么一大把胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这人穿的还是阿伊努人的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,原来戴那顶帽子的骑手跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你会不会骑马?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,马主要求骑手作假 结果骑手跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那个马主是黑道老大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他想让没大气的马赢下比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:12:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,万一搞砸了 我们都会遭到他的报复
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在比赛前给这匹马喂大量的水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这样它的速度会明显慢下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你正常骑就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你明明想赢对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 好好按住它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,按计划是它赢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用水兑蝮蛇粉 再用橡皮管灌进马的鼻子里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有时管子不小心塞进气管里 马就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们押我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,胡子剃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等下再和你们解释
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一场比赛我会骑3号马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,茵卡拉玛大人 请您占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,指引迷茫的小人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,希拉奇卡姆依说3号不会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,白石 收手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在迷茫不知如何判断的时候我们才会用到占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这场旅途没有一丝迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所以也不需要占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,希拉奇卡姆依说6号会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,6号是吧 我全押了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,白石 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好歹把买炸药的钱留下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我要拼一回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,茵卡拉玛大人 帮我去买
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,收到~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你来北海道还不是想赚钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要多少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能是两万贯金子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,母狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来阻止我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可我买了 全押的6号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不过对你来说 没中反倒更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人要是赚了大钱 还会帮阿希莉帕妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有发财的路子 还不需要你赌命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有了足够的钱我就先跑路了 你觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这种话我会对那姑娘说吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,颜色和你父亲一样美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们后会有期 阿希莉帕妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这匹马叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,烈风
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了 赢的是6号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,6号不是第一 我们全得死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这桶水记得让烈风喝光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走 烈风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,6号 靠你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,输了我就剁了你做马肉火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,6号冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,基罗兰克晚走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,看我说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,冲啊 烈风 跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,3号那是什么骑法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.91,Explain,,0,0,0,,这是到了现代成为主流的撅腚鞍骑法 俗称猴子骑\N这种臀部悬空身体前倾的骑法不会使骑手的体重完全落在马背上\N从而减少了马匹的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这一张买的3号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,冲 烈风 跑跑跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,冲啊 基罗兰克!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,冲啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,现在输惨了的黑道老大肯定在到处找我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,白石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里发神经
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,别管他 他自己会跟上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶 发大财了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,被狐狸骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们找的是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我来这里只是因为碰巧听说这里有文身人皮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你们经过理发店我一眼就认出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前在鹤见中尉手下干活 所以很了解你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,需要得力的保镖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,土方岁三先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,拉屎王 醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉自己做了一场噩梦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,赌博千万不能沾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我反省过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪里反省了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快做准备 离网走还远着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,先别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要听我的绝密情报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不会又是什么无聊的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,薄野的一位漂亮姑娘告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一个月前 有个男人来到旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男人是个贼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天他溜进一栋房子行窃时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,发现了十分诡异的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有许多用死人做成的标本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他还看到了一张不是黑道文身的文身人皮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,姑娘说那栋房子在夕张
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这趟去网走的旅途不一定顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果在路上打听到文身人皮的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就应该去探个究竟才是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,夕张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这边手里有五个人的文身暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,鹤见中尉至少有一张人皮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道他有没有找到别的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.43,0:22:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,月岛军曹盯着那座坟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天才发生矿难 那座土坟刚挖好没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.44,0:22:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,会上钩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.65,0:22:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一有矿难 消息瞬间就会传遍整个夕张
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那个盗墓犯肯定也知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 二阶堂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,洋平的耳朵和鹤见中尉一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.62,0:22:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可以把鹤见中尉的左耳给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一只太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:23:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了知道了 等我死了就给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.92,0:23:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,鹤见中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.43,0:23:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 鹤见中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,追
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,别打死他啊 二阶堂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.61,0:23:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,掉的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还给失主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:28.88,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}I realize desire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:32.47,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}And trembling in the anger
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:36.55,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Though I know that you're a great liar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:40.22,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}The world is painted in dark grey
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:46.94,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}混乱の時代や嘘と暴力の螺旋が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:54.91,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}どうか貴方の未来へと陰落とさぬ様に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:02:02.33,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Going down to reach somewhere together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:08.59,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}もう一度 夢見るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:11.76,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Someday we will find out the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:19.01,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}この傷の数だけ 闇夜を駆け抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:22.68,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}踊る Long and winding road
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:26.23,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Standing on the cutting edge of life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:30.07,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Holding a rusty old knife
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:33.61,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}朝陽が射し示すまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:37.28,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}駆ける Long and winding road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:28.88,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}欲望在我心中咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:32.47,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}我在愤怒中颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:36.55,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}尽管我知道你是个大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:40.22,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}世界却早已被染上一层深灰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:46.94,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}这个混乱的时代 交织着谎言与暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:54.91,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}希望它们不要为你的未来蒙上阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:02:02.33,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}让我们一起坚持 抵达一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:08.59,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}然后再做一次梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:11.76,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}有一天我们会找到真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:19.01,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}有多少伤痕 便跨过多少黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:22.68,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}在这条漫长曲折的路上起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:26.23,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}拼搏在生死一线间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:30.07,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}握住那生锈的旧匕首
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:33.61,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}直至晨光洒向大地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:37.28,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}在这条漫长曲折的路上奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:04.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,夜を刺す無数の遠吠えが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:08.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,天を貫いた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:14.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,僕らみんなたった一つの満月に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:19.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,そうやって手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:23.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,目的地の消された地図持って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:26.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,燃える炎 交わし合って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:29.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,荒れた未来図は 続いてるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,痛みもぜんぶ受け取って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:41.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,連れていくんだと 深く胸に誓って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:43.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ぶつかって 傷付いて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:46.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,いつかまた、ここに来るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,一切の現実も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:52.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,燃え尽きれば美しい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:57.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,駆け抜ける 白の世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:05.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,迷いを捨てた火花が今、散った
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:04.60,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,将夜晚刺穿的无数嗷叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:08.77,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,贯穿了天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:14.91,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,我们大家都向着唯一的满月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:19.29,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,像这样将手伸出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:23.62,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,拿着被消去目的地的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:26.14,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,燃烧的火焰互相交错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:29.29,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,未来虽然还模糊 但还是会继续
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.82,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,哪怕需要承受全部的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:41.23,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,也要将其带走深深地在胸中发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:43.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,历经挫折受过伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:46.21,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,总有一天会再来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.66,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,现实的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:52.93,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,付之一炬 才是美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:57.75,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,奔跑在这纯白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:05.97,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,舍弃迷茫的火花绚烂绽放在这一刻
